high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the trash bin.
Take the tomato from the trash bin.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to go to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to face the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the trash can.
Take the tomato out of the trash can.
Turn around and veer right to the sink.
Heat the tomato in the microwave above the sink.
Turn around and walk right to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge on the third shelf to the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left go to the dust bin.
Pick up the tomato from inside the dust bin.
Turn around and walk towards the wash basin then turn right in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato in the microwave then cook it for 7 seconds and the open the microwave and take out the tomato.
Turn around go towards the fridge then turn right facing to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the tomato on the third shelf and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Take out the tomato from dust bin and put it into the Fridge.
